        "text": "And all Israel were bringing.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " Samuel has “and David and all the house of Israel,” and “ark of the Lord.”",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Cornet.—Rather, trumpet.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "Cornet.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
