            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "trumpet.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The rest of this verse is wanting in Samuel, but all the additional instruments have already been mentioned (1Chronicles 15:16-21).",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "The rest of this verse is wanting in Samuel, but all the additional instruments have already been mentioned (",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "1Chronicles 15:16-21",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ").",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Trumpets.—Clarions, or straight trumpets.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "Trumpets.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—Clarions, or straight trumpets.",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The last clause should be rendered, “and with clanging cymbals, with harps and lutes.” (Comp. Psalm 150:3-4.)",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "The last clause should be rendered, “and with clanging cymbals, with harps and lutes.” (Comp. ",
            "children": []
          },
